Title: AKA You're a Winner!
Writer: Brian Michael Bendis (based on the character from the Marvel comics by), Michael Gaydos (based on the character from the Marvel comics by), Melissa Rosenberg (created by), Edward Ricourt, Jenna Reback (staff writer)
Actors: Krysten Ritter, Mike Colter, Erin Moriarty, Eka Darville
Plot: Luke hires Jessica to help him find someone who may have skipped town, but she fears he'll learn too much about her history in the process.
